    "source": "app/static/styles.css :root (captured 2026-05-22)",
    "tokenConvention": "Every color key maps to a CSS custom property named --<key>. e.g. \"accent\" -> var(--accent). The group names (surfaces, lines, text, accents, crystals, states) are for human organization only and are NOT part of the variable name. An ingester should flatten all groups and emit `--<key>: <value>;` into :root. The four crystal-* tokens are extra identity colors; wire them up where supported.",
    "notExportedYet": "Non-color :root tokens still live only in styles.css and are intentionally omitted here: --radius (12px), --radius-s (8px), --shadow (0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.38)). The ~37 hex + 38 rgba() literals scattered through styles.css (gradients, focus glows, #fff, etc.) are also not yet tokenized; promote them into this file when wiring up ingestion.",
